sequenceDiagram
  participant RX as USART RX
  participant IRQ as drv_usartN_irq
  participant Dev as usartN device
  participant Ind as agc_shell_rx_ind
  participant Ring as input ringbuffer
  participant Sem as rx_sem
  participant Thread as shell thread

  RX->>IRQ: RX interrupt
  IRQ->>IRQ: status.empty == 0
  IRQ->>Dev: rx_indicate(dev, 1)
  Dev->>Ind: callback
  Ind->>Dev: rt_device_read()
  Dev-->>Ind: input bytes
  Ind->>Ring: put bytes
  Ind->>Sem: rt_sem_release()
  Sem->>Thread: wake shell
  Thread->>Thread: parse and execute command
